Package: pisicevir
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${python3:Depends},
 binutils,
 python3-yaml,
 python3-pydantic
Description: external package importer and PISI recipe generator
 Pisicevir inspects external package artifacts, classifies conversion risk,
 and generates native PISI packaging projects. Debian package inspection is
 the first supported source adapter.

Package: pisicevir-gui
Section: devel
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 pisicevir (= ${binary:Version}),
 python3-pyqt5
Description: graphical workbench for Pisicevir
 This package provides the Qt graphical interface for inspecting Debian
 packages and reviewing generated PISI recipe data.
